BosKone auction, signed by many of the writers, including Roger Zelazny. The set went for $150, not a high price, considering the condition of the set and the signatures.<br /><br />INSIDE STRAIGHT is the beginning of a new generation, it's 'not your father's WILD CARDS'. Give it a try, and see how you like it, and if you do, then go searching for all those earlier books. If this series goes well for TOR, then we may see more reissues and more new books set in the present/future.<br /><br />We're beginning to call the clans to gather for the mega-WILD CARDS signing party at Page One in Albuquerque on Feb 2. Looks like it's going to be one to remember, with many members of the Wild Cards Consortium in attendance.<br /><br />I'll be the one wearing the Radha O'Reilly custom airbrushed t-shirt.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"9 years ago","ctime":"January 5 2008, 05:34:31 UTC","parent":3029792,"massactions":0,"subject":"not at this time but","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://parrismcb.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"parrismcb","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"parrismcb","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://parrismcb.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"parrismcb","ctime_ts":1199511271,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/69379274/13498564","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/29984.html?replyto=3029024","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/29984.html?thread=3029024#t3029024","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/29984.html?thread=3029024#t3029024","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/29984.html?